summary: Writer for hire
body:
Writer for hire

I’m attempting to start a blog just for my writing, my only problem is I have a hard time writing for myself - i.e. I used to write two to five little drabbles for my friend everyday in high school, where as my ao3 account has a whopping 5 works posted in three years. 

Which is where some of you lovely people hopefully come in.

Send me your ideas, the good, the bad, and/or the complete crack; and I’ll see what weird and wonderfulness I can turn out for you

summary: A big thank you
title: A big thank you
body:
To everyone that has read/liked/reblogged my stories! 

YEARS ago I wrote and posted (on AO3 and fanfiction.net) a couple of OC stories (Both with Dean), they are a rough read but overall good stories. I think I’m going to rewrite them to be reader insert and change a few things. If anyone wanted to be tagged just let me know. 

I just started on a Bucky x Reader fic too!

Also, willing to try out more one-shots to get myself in the groove of writing again. Have any requests?  Right now I’m doing pairings for Dean, Sam and Cas from Supernatural. Bucky Barnes, Steve Rodgers, or even Stucky from Marvel. Willing to try just about anything though.

Thanks again everyone!
